      "rationale": "All three FEA implementations (FDA in-house, Ansys Mechanical, DePuy Synthes) operate under documented software quality management systems with version control, regression testing, and traceability to requirements. Achieved level exceeds the required level for Model Risk 3."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
